<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_fgs_b2w_t3c">
    <title>8. Prompt Construction</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>The system constructs a structured prompt using retrieved chunks.</p>
        <section id="section_cbm_c2w_t3c">
            <title>Format</title>
            <pre>DOCUMENT: &lt;document_path>
SECTION: &lt;title>

&lt;content></pre>
            <p>Multiple sections are concatenated to form the context.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <title>Prompt Rules</title>
            <ul id="ul_yqq_32w_t3c">
                <li>Use only provided documentation </li>
                <li>Do not hallucinate information </li>
                <li>Combine information across sections when necessary </li>
                <li>Prefer explicit grounding in source content</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
